<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-TW">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>五月日本行｜分帳入口</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-color: #ff4757; /* 櫻花粉紅 */
            --bg-color: #f8f9fa;
            --text-dark: #2f3542;
        }
        body {
            font-family: "PingFang TC", "Microsoft JhengHei", sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--bg-color);
            margin: 0;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            color: var(--text-dark);
            text-align: center;
        }
        .hero-card {
            background: white;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            width: 90%;
            max-width: 400px;
            border-radius: 24px;
            box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .icon {
            font-size: 60px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            color: var(--text-dark);
        }
        p {
            color: #747d8c;
            margin: 10px 0 30px 0;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        .btn-start {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff4757, #ff6b81);
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 16px 40px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(255, 71, 87, 0.3);
            transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
        }
        .btn-start:active {
            transform: scale(0.95);
            box-shadow: 0 5px 10px rgba(255, 71, 87, 0.2);
        }
        .features {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 15px;
            margin-top: 40px;
            text-align: left;
        }
        .feat-item {
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            background: #f1f2f6;
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .feat-item span { margin-right: 8px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="hero-card">
    <div class="icon">🇯🇵</div>
    <h1>五月日本旅遊</h1>
    <p>匯率換算 · 多人分帳 · 一鍵分享<br>讓旅行的帳目簡簡單單。</p>
    
    <a href="split_tool.html" class="btn-start">開始記帳</a>

    <div class="features">
        <div class="feat-item"><span>💴</span> 即時匯率</div>
        <div class="feat-item"><span>✅</span> 勾選分攤</div>
        <div class="feat-item"><span>🔗</span> 網址分享</div>
        <div class="feat-item"><span>📊</span> 試算表匯出</div>
    </div>
    
    <div style="margin-top: 30px; font-size: 0.7rem; color: #ced4da;">
        v1.0｜專為五月三人行設計
    </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
